            "code": "from scipy.optimize import fsolve\r\nimport numpy as np\r\n\r\n# Define the equation\r\ndef equation(x):\r\n    return np.sin(x) + x**2 - 42\r\n\r\n# Initial guess: since x^2 is large, let's guess x ~ sqrt(42)\r\nx_initial_guesses = [6, -6]  # sqrt(42) ≈ 6.5, try positive and negative\r\n\r\n# Solve\r\nsolutions = [fsolve(equation, guess)[0] for guess in x_initial_guesses]\r\nsolutions",
